dc_description_s: Shows soil types, school houses, cemeteries, churches, railroads, county roads and township roads. Detached from: Soil survey of Morgan County / J.B. Edmondson. In 36th Annual report of Department of Geology and Natural Resources, Indiana. Scale approximately 1:63,360. Not 1/2 in. per mile Soil surveyed by J.B. Edmondson, 1911.
